role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">风暴吞没白昼化作黑夜</span></p><p begin="02:18.549" end="02:20.776" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="02:18.549" end="02:18.858">I'll</span> <span begin="02:18.858" end="02:19.184">guide</span> <span begin="02:19.184" end="02:19.433">you</span> <span begin="02:19.433" end="02:19.839">through</span> <span begin="02:19.839" end="02:20.059">the</span> <span begin="02:20.059" end="02:20.776">lightning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我将引你穿越电光</span></p><p begin="02:20.776" end="02:23.248" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="02:20.776" end="02:21.368">Stay</span> <span begin="02:21.368" end="02:22.061">close</span> <span begin="02:22.061" end="02:22.719">by</span> <span begin="02:22.719" end="02:23.012">my</span> <span begin="02:23.012" end="02:23.248">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请紧靠我身旁</span></p><p begin="02:24.583" end="02:29.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="02:24.583" end="02:24.934">Up</span> <span begin="02:24.934" end="02:25.292">in</span> <span begin="02:25.292" end="02:25.494">the</span> <span begin="02:25.494" end="02:26.604">clouds,</span> <span begin="02:26.604" end="02:26.893">I</span> <span begin="02:26.893" end="02:27.873">found</span> <span begin="02:27.873" end="02:28.118">my</span> <span begin="02:28.118" end="02:29.060">voice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在云端之上，我寻得自己的声音</span></p><p begin="02:29.702" end="02:34.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="02:29.702" end="02:30.032">Up</span> <span begin="02:30.032" end="02:30.336">past</span> <span begin="02:30.336" end="02:30.484">the</span> <span begin="02:30.484" end="02:31.612">shouts</span> <span begin="02:31.612" end="02:31.928">and</span> <span begin="02:31.928" end="02:33.267">broken</span> <span begin="02:33.267" end="02:34.180">noise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">冲破喧嚣与破碎的嘈杂</span></p><p begin="02:34.470" end="02:36.778" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="02:34.470" end="02:34.829">So</span> <span begin="02:34.829" end="02:35.132">don't</span> <span begin="02:35.132" end="02:35.486">let</span> <span begin="02:35.486" end="02:35.680">me</span> <span begin="02:35.680" end="02:36.778">fall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">别让我坠落</span></p><p begin="02:37.092" end="02:39.541" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="02:37.092" end="02:37.446">Where</span> <span begin="02:37.446" end="02:37.711">I</span> <span begin="02:37.711" end="02:38.083">don't</span> <span begin="02:38.083" end="02:39.541">belong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坠入不属于我的地方</span></p><p begin="02:39.983" end="02:44.788" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="02:39.983" end="02:40.241">I</span> <span begin="02:40.241" end="02:40.607">can't</span> <span begin="02:40.607" end="02:40.906">go</span> <span begin="02:40.906" end="02:41.830">back</span> <span begin="02:41.830" end="02:42.218">and</span> <span begin="02:42.218" end="02:43.120">lose</span> <span begin="02:43.120" end="02:43.548">it</span> <span begin="02:43.548" end="02:44.788">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我无法重回过往失去一切</span></p></div></body></tt>